code: public void testSecurityServerTransportServiceWrapsAllHandlers() {     for (TransportService transportService : internalCluster().getInstances(TransportService.class)) {         RequestHandlerRegistry handler = transportService.transport.getRequestHandler(TransportService.HANDSHAKE_ACTION_NAME).         assertEquals("handler not wrapped by " + SecurityServerTransportInterceptor.ProfileSecuredRequestHandler.class + ". do all the handler registration methods have overrides?", handler.toString(), "ProfileSecuredRequestHandler{action='" + handler.getAction() + "', executorName='" + handler.getExecutor() + "', forceExecution=" + handler.isForceExecution() + "}").     } }
